| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5532 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6c1c4820-0162-53d4-b822-1b49c4e8120c"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
